{
  "stem": "7938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you work, you had a chance to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you didn't work, you wouldn't go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they wouldn't allow you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Except is there were some people who, who had big interests-- they were big manufacturers-- who were a big interest in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they allowed for these people, if they paid some amount, some big sums to the-- to the Judenrat, that they will get permission to stay either in ghetto, or even outside of the ghetto if needed.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The head of the-- of the-- not of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of the Judenrat--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat-- the head of the Judenrat was Marek Beiberstein.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- a commission was created, with three consisted, consisted of three members.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German administration.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was a delegate of the German administration of the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was the Germ-- a delegate of the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one was the delegate of the Jewish population, which was the president, the Judenrat president.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they started taking applications with the sums of money which everybody had to pay.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody had to show why he wants to stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course there were a lot of people who put the money in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this whole deal became sour after a few, few weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they levied a different sum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew how much-- as much as somebody could afford.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And during the first week, or two weeks, everyone-- everything went all right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Applications were reviewed, and certain permissions were given, certain denied.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after this time, the German representative approached the Jewish representative and he told him that from now on, unless he gets some money from the money which is collected, no one of these applications will be approved.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the German was Reichert.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
